snippet.title: Fast Math Trick to subtacting numbers mentally - two digit numbers
snippet.description: Mental maths is easy - this fast math trick will show you how to (almost) instantly subtract two digit numbers.  Three digit numbers will be shown in the next video. To donate to the tecmath channel:  https://paypal.me/tecmath?locale.x=en_AU
